data [19-22] using the equation given in summary table 1-C.
The tables of vapor pressure are based on an analysis of the data in references 23 - 30, which
are arranged roughly in order of the weight given to the data taken from them. The accepted triple
and boiling points are those of Frank , et al., [25] whose work makes it almost certain that
